# ============================================================================
# Personal OS — repo .gitignore
# Goal: it must be STRUCTURALLY IMPOSSIBLE to commit anyone's vault DATA.
# Only the scaffold structure, templates and curated examples are tracked.
# ============================================================================

# --- vault-scaffold ships STRUCTURE ONLY. Ignore everything inside it, then
#     re-include just the structural files via ! allow-patterns. A real note
#     dropped into vault-scaffold/lessons/ therefore cannot be staged. --------
vault-scaffold/**
!vault-scaffold/CLAUDE.md
!vault-scaffold/HOME.example.md
!vault-scaffold/.gitignore
!vault-scaffold/.graphifyignore
!vault-scaffold/_templates/
!vault-scaffold/_templates/**
!vault-scaffold/**/
!vault-scaffold/**/.gitkeep

# --- Runtime logs & state — never, anywhere ---------------------------------
**/lesson-fires.jsonl
**/*-hooks.log
**/.chat_import_state.json
**/.chat_mining_state.txt
**/.chat_mining_state.json
**/.chatgpt_import_state.json
**/.chatgpt_mining_state.txt
**/harvest-queue.jsonl
**/health.json
**/dream-cursor.json
**/dream-embeds.json
**/dream-feedback.jsonl
**/install-manifest.json

# --- Live Claude Code state (in case someone runs this inside ~/.claude) -----
**/history.jsonl
**/sessions/
**/projects/
**/settings.local.json
**/stats-cache.json
**/policy-limits.json
**/shell-snapshots/

# --- Machine-generated indexes / graphs -------------------------------------
graphify-out/
**/graphify-out/
.cache/qmd/
**/.graphify_labels.json

# --- Python / tooling --------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/

# --- OS / editor -------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.obsidian/workspace*
.obsidian/cache
